OL,3,CMemory stones for Covid bereaved
OL,5,FDozens of families bereaved by covid,
OL,6,For during the coronavirus pandemic,
OL,7,Fhave come together for a service of
OL,8,Fpoetry, song, silence and reflection
OL,9,Fmarking the national day of Covid-19
OL,10,Fremembrance.
OL,12,FThere were emotional scenes as
OL,13,Frelatives, some of whom have never
OL,14,Fspoken publicly about their loss,
OL,15,Fshared their stories of love and loss.
OL,17,FThe stage was set surrounding a heart
OL,18,Fshape made out of hundreds of
OL,19,Fpersonalised stones depicting the
OL,20,Fpeople who passed away during the
OL,21,Fpandemic.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
