OL,3,CMemory stones for Covid bereaved
OL,5,FThe display by the group "Memory
OL,6,FStones of Love" each tell a story of
OL,7,Fwho these people were in their lives.
OL,9,FThose in attendance wish for these to
OL,10,Fbe given a permanent home in a
OL,11,Fmonument of sorts, so that they can go
OL,12,Fand see the display any time, as
OL,13,FBrenda Doherty from the group
OL,14,Fexplained.
OL,16,FMany present said that they continue
OL,17,Fregret the fact their grieving process
OL,18,Fwas never complete because they did
OL,19,Fnot have the opportunity to hold wakes
OL,20,Fand funerals.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
