OL,3,CMemory stones for Covid bereaved
OL,5,FThis is a pain that Hazel Gray knows
OL,6,Fonly too well as she had to endure the
OL,7,Fordeal twice, having lost both her
OL,8,Fmother and her father during periods
OL,9,Fof restrictions.
OL,11,F"People lined the roads, that's all
OL,12,Fthat they could do," she said.
OL,14,F"We had no sandwiches, no wake in the
OL,15,Fhouse, no endless cups of tea, no
OL,16,Freminiscing about yesteryear, there's
OL,17,Fso many things i wish people could
OL,18,Fhave told me about, stories and things
OL,19,Flike that, and none of that happened,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
