OL,3,CMemory stones for Covid bereaved
OL,5,F"I'm almost envious now of people who
OL,6,Fget a proper funeral because I know
OL,7,Fthat twice, I didn't get that."
OL,9,FHer mum's memory stone features her
OL,10,Fknitting work, while her dad's paints
OL,11,Fa picture of a farming man with a
OL,12,Fgreat love of marching bands. She said
OL,13,Fshe appreciated this event more than
OL,14,Fwords can say.
OL,16,F"I'm an only child, and I didn't have
OL,17,Fa lot of people to share the grief
OL,18,Fwith," said Hazel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
