OL,5,FThey have welcomed finding a group who
OL,6,Funderstands their loss.
OL,8,F"I had to put her on the iPad and that
OL,9,Fwas how everybody said their goodbyes
OL,10,Fto her," said Janine.
OL,12,F"She wasn't able to talk, to say hello
OL,13,For anything, it was horrific.
OL,15,F"She shouldn't have been left on her
OL,16,Fown in there those two weeks she was
OL,17,Faway," she said, visibly heartbroken
OL,18,Frecalling it all.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
