OL,5,F"I know she would have been frightened
OL,6,Fand scared, but she as such a strong
OL,7,Fperson, she would never have said."
OL,9,FThe sisters shared some happy memories
OL,10,Fof their mother too during this
OL,11,Fdevastating interview.
OL,13,F"She was a breath of fresh air,
OL,14,Fbubbly, entertaining, loved people,
OL,15,Fwas that listening person, was always
OL,16,Fthere, and there was never bad days
OL,17,Fbecause mummy would have said
OL,18,Fsomething and taken you out of it and
OL,19,Fhugged you," they recalled.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
