OL,3,CMemory stones for Covid bereaved
OL,5,FBaby Ziggy's life ended when it was
OL,6,Fonly just getting started.
OL,8,FThe infant's mother, Catherine Todd,
OL,9,Fagreed that a lack of access to
OL,10,Fsupport at the time of her son's
OL,11,Fpassing caused hurt and she was also
OL,12,Fglad to find a group with such
OL,13,Fsolidarity for her loss.
OL,15,F"I feel like me and him really bonded,
OL,16,Fand I know that he's around us and
OL,17,Fwe've now got to other babies and I
OL,18,Fknow he watches out for us all.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
