OL,5,F"Because we have really got a lot of
OL,6,Fsupport after Ziggy passed and I feel
OL,7,Fthings like this just kind of brings
OL,8,Feveryone together, you know, we're all
OL,9,Fin the same situation, we have
OL,10,Fdifferent stories, but it is really
OL,11,Fnice."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, landmarks across NI were
OL,14,Filluminated in yellow on Sunday
OL,15,Fevening to mark the nationwide day of
OL,16,Freflection.
